1
00:00:03,090 --> 00:00:04,330
Previously on "The Mentalist"...

2
00:00:05,020 --> 00:00:10,230
Ten years ago,the serial killer known
as Red John killed my wife and daughter.

3
00:00:14,150 --> 00:00:16,660
We've been hunting for him ever since.

4
00:00:16,810 --> 00:00:18,970
We call ourselves the Blake association.

5
00:00:19,200 --> 00:00:21,060
Well,who else is in the association?

6
00:00:21,200 --> 00:00:22,980
Cops,judges,F.B.I.
agents--

7
00:00:23,110 --> 00:00:25,860
anyone in law enforcement
that needs a secret covered up.

8
00:00:25,960 --> 00:00:27,580
A secret society of dirty cops.

9
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:29,560
And Red John's a member.

10
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:33,850
Kira Tinsley told me
something before she passed.

11
00:00:33,930 --> 00:00:36,460
She told me that her
killer-- Red John--

12
00:00:36,540 --> 00:00:40,120
has a tattoo-- three
dots on his left arm.

13
00:00:41,290 --> 00:00:42,470
So who's Red John?

14
00:00:42,600 --> 00:00:47,520
Today we're pleased to announce that
we--we finally have a name,a face.

15
00:00:47,730 --> 00:00:52,840
The director of the division of law
enforcement,Gail Bertram,is Red John.

16
00:00:53,490 --> 00:00:58,050
I am holding in my hand a
writ from a federal judge.

17
00:00:58,540 --> 00:01:01,800
The F.B.I. is closing down
your organization right now.

18
00:01:02,610 --> 00:01:05,280
We're done.There's
nothing more to do here.

19
00:01:05,370 --> 00:01:07,970
You're not quitting.I don't believe it.

20
00:01:07,970 --> 00:01:10,040
It's out of our hands for now.

21
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:12,430
I'll be in touch.Okay?

22
00:01:13,590 --> 00:01:15,820
I'm sorry. For everything.

23
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:47,320
Lisbon.Glad you can join us.

24
00:01:47,830 --> 00:01:49,090
Traffic.

25
00:01:50,350 --> 00:01:51,450
Where's Jane?

26
00:01:51,550 --> 00:01:53,850
He'll be in to see you
as soon as he's able.

27
00:01:55,060 --> 00:01:56,710
This way.

28
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:10,850
Please,take a seat.

29
00:02:14,930 --> 00:02:16,600
Boy,this is a mess,huh?

30
00:02:17,150 --> 00:02:19,370
A big mess.

31
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:21,110
- Look,I think we all--
you can talk later.

32
00:02:23,280 --> 00:02:29,910
Now I understand... You
must all feel scared,nervous.

33
00:02:30,830 --> 00:02:33,390
Don't know what in the hell
is gonna happen next,right?

34
00:02:33,550 --> 00:02:36,680
- Agent-- So let me
explain what's next.

35
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:44,020
Over the next few days,we will be
talking to each of you... individually.

36
00:02:44,630 --> 00:02:50,830
You are entitled to bring along an attorney
or a union rep,should you so choose.

37
00:02:50,920 --> 00:02:53,140
Why would we need an attorney?

38
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:57,270
Well,let's look at this
from our perspective,Kimball.

39
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:59,950
Your boss Bertram is a criminal.

40
00:03:00,730 --> 00:03:03,090
Makes sense that you might be one,too.

41
00:03:03,450 --> 00:03:06,790
We will be looking very
closely at all of you.

42
00:03:06,980 --> 00:03:11,550
If you have ever done anything
even remotely questionable,

43
00:03:11,990 --> 00:03:16,050
we will find out,and we will prosecute.

44
00:03:17,870 --> 00:03:22,910
Unless,of course,we feel very,very
comfortable with your cooperation.

45
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,520
Then you got a little wiggle room.

46
00:03:31,780 --> 00:03:34,550
***

47
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:36,910
The F.B.I. is overseeing
 an international manhunt

48
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:41,130
for prominent Sacramento law
enforcement official  Gail Bertram.

49
00:03:41,230 --> 00:03:46,140
F.B.I. sources confirm that Bertram  is believed
